715178f-a.title: Manhattan: 118th Street - Madison Avenue
715178f-a.text:
118th Street, adjoining the northeast corner of Madison -venue,
showing old frame building.
P. L. Sperr  July 9, 1941
NO REPRODUCTIONS

715176f-a.title: Manhattan: 118th Street (East) - Madison Avenue
715176f-a.text:
49-57 East 118th Street, at, adjoining, and east of the
N.E. corner of Madison Avenue. No. 53 is a three-story frame
house with a stucco front.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 544
